Insider Activity


Individual




Stanley J. Meresman



Mr. Stanley J. Meresman is Independent Class III Director at LinkedIn Corp. and Independent Director at HyTrust, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Palo Alto Networks, Inc., LinkedIn Corp., HyTrust, Inc., and Medallia, Inc.
Mr. Meresman was previously employed as Independent Director by Zynga, Inc., Independent Director by Meru Networks, Inc., Independent Director by Riverbed Technology, Inc., Venture Partner by TCMI, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by Silicon Graphics, Inc., an Advisor by Inktomi Corp., an Advisor by RealNetworks, Inc., an Advisor by Silicon Image, Inc., and Chief Financial Officer & VP-Administration by Cypress Semiconductor Corp. He also served on the board at Turn, Inc., Polycom, Inc., Force10 Networks, Inc., LightSurf Technologies, Inc., ModCloth, Inc., Starfish Software, Inc., and VMware, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of California, Berkeley and an MBA from the Stanford Graduate School of Business.



