Stanley J. Meresman, MBA

Age : 69Public asset : 2,074,590 USDLinked companies :  Palo Alto Networks Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Stanley J. Meresman is on the Board of Directors at Palo Alto Networks, Inc., Medallia, Inc., Saama Technologies, Inc. and HyTrust, Inc. Mr. Meresman was previously employed as an Independent Director by Zynga, Inc., an Independent Director by LinkedIn Corp., an Independent Director by Meru Networks, Inc., an Independent Director by Riverbed Technology, Inc., Venture Partner by TCMI, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by Silicon Graphics, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & VP-Administration by Cypress Semiconductor Corp., an Advisor by Inktomi Corp., an Advisor by RealNetworks, Inc., and an Advisor by Silicon Image, Inc.He also served on the board at Turn, Inc., Polycom, Inc., Force10 Networks, Inc., LightSurf Technologies, Inc., ModCloth, Inc., Starfish Software, Inc. and VMware, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from the University of California, Berkeley and an MBA from Stanford Graduate School of Business.



